---
description: Require short file headers for new files
alwaysApply: true
---

When creating a NEW file, always add a short header comment at the top (8–15 lines max) that includes:

- Purpose (1 sentence)
- Where it is used/called from (hook/controller/service/template)
- Inputs/Outputs or key variables
- Side effects (DB writes, cache, external calls) if any

Do not add headers to generated files or tiny style partials unless requested.
Keep headers factual and project-specific.
